item.title: Sample Knowledge Page
item.description: Sample Knowledge Page This is an example article. It is intended to demonstrate some of the key styling elements for KnowledgeBase, the knowledge base static website sample by Christie Templeton. Why choose KnowledgeBase? KnowledgeBase is a Hugo theme customized by Christie Templeton, which is based off of the Porting Grav Learn theme and the Knowall Wordpress theme. This site serves as a help center for your product or service. It organises your content into a knowledge base where customers, employees, and vendors can access support articles 24/7, be that documentation, FAQs, videos, LMS training, or tutorials.
